What

Many are getting on the Web3 bandwagon, but even more are left behind. We want to level the playing field! Our ecosystem not only helps you get involved in and benefit from the Web3 space, it's for empowerment...for social and environmental impact, for access and inclusion.

Who

All Creators On & Offline

Use your talent for impact. Create your own portfolio and earn, retain royalties, monetize content, or contribute to calls for collaborations

Natives & Newbies

Natives- use your know-how for good. Get stuck in & support impact! Newbies- we help with quality curated content to get you up to speed & active... or we can mint buy, sell or store for you!

Influencers & Fans

Stream, ticket, trade, create, commission and store content & experiences. Use your power and influence for good! Go on, you know you want to!

Corporates Making an Impact

Step into the World of Web3, align your NFT launches, tokens & more with vetted impact & communities of support. If you're not sure where to start, we're here to help!

Impact Org for & Non Profit

Does what you do benefit People or Planet? Get vetted & launch a campaign with or without your own NFT collection. Call for collaborations, & creators for impact can help!

How

Do it yourself

Whether you know what to do or want a step-by-step walkthrough to do it yourself, you can hop right in and start your Web 3 for impact journey here!

Done for you

Want to create, buy or sell an NFT or collection, or create & launch your Web 3 products and services, but don't want to do it yourself? As long as it's impact-aligned, we can do it all for you!

NFT for Impact Basics

Create your collection

Set up your wallet

Once you've set up your wallet of choice, connect it to OpsnSea by cliking the NFT Morket place in the top right corner.

Add Your NFTs

Upload your work (imoge,video, audio, or 3D art), add a title and description, and custom. your NFTs. with properties.

List them for sale

Choose between auctions, fixed-price listings, and declining-price listings. You choose how you want to sell your NFTs!
